{
  "id": "69bb0ad7a80438487524a7d5",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:たらい回し",
  "created": 1773865731,
  "updated": 1773865752,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69bb0ad7a80438487524a7d5",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:たらい回し",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865731,
      "updated": 1773865731
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b030000000000957be9",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865731,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bea",
      "text": "「はいはーい！今日のテーマは『[たらい回し]』ね〜。これ、リアルでもネットでもよく見るやつじゃん？“それ担当じゃないんで〜”ってやつｗ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957beb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bec",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bed",
      "text": "「ええ、とても身近な言葉ですわね。まるで行き場のない舟が、波に押されて漂うように……誰の手にも受け止めてもらえない、そんな寂しさを感じます」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bef",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bf0",
      "text": "「定義から整理しよう。“たらい回し”は、責任主体が曖昧なまま、対応が複数の担当者間で転送され続ける現象。組織設計の不備や権限分散が主因」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bf1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bf2",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bf3",
      "text": "「うわ出た、りかのガチ解説ｗ でもさ、ユーザー目線だと“いいから誰かやってくれ！”って感じじゃん？問い合わせして、3回くらい転送されたらもうHPゼロなんだけど」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bf4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bf5",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bf6",
      "text": "「そのお気持ち、とてもよくわかりますわ。誰かに助けを求めたのに、さらに遠ざけられてしまうようで……心が少し冷えてしまいますものね（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bf7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bf8",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bf9",
      "text": "「感情的コストは無視できない。顧客満足度、いわゆるCSの低下に直結する。例えば、カスタマーサポート設計のベストプラクティスでは“ワンストップ解決率”が重要指標になる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bfa",
      "text": "参考: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Customer_service 」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bfb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bfc",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bfd",
      "text": "「ワンストップって“1回で終わらせろよ”ってこと？シンプルで助かる〜」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bfe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957bff",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c00",
      "text": "「その理解で問題ない。要は“最初に受けた人が最後まで責任を持つ”設計」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c01",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c02",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c03",
      "text": "「それは、とても安心できますわね。一度差し出した手を、最後まで離さない……そんな誠実さを感じます」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c04",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c05",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c06",
      "text": "「でもさ、現実は“それうちの部署じゃないんで”ってパスされがちじゃん？あれ何でなん？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c07",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c08",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c09",
      "text": "「構造的問題。主に三つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c0a",
      "text": " 1. 役割分担が細かすぎる（サイロ化）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c0b",
      "text": " 2. 評価制度が個別最適（自分の仕事だけやればいい）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c0c",
      "text": " 3. 責任の所在が不明確",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c0d",
      "text": "この三つが揃うと、たらい回しは発生しやすい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c0e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c0f",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c10",
      "text": "「まるで、細かく区切られた庭園のようですわね。それぞれが自分の区画を守るあまり、全体の景色が見えなくなってしまう……」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c11",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c12",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c13",
      "text": "「うまいこと言う〜。でもそれってさ、働いてる人が悪いってより、仕組みの問題じゃね？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c14",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c15",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c16",
      "text": "「同意。個人の善意に依存する設計は脆弱。システムで防ぐべき。例えば“エスカレーションルール”や“担当オーナー制”を明確にする」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c17",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c18",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c19",
      "text": "「オーナー制って、“この件はあなたがラスボスね”って決めるやつ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c1a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c1b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c1c",
      "text": "「概ね正しい。最終責任者を固定することで、処理の発散を防ぐ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c1d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c1e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c1f",
      "text": "「責任を引き受けるというのは、勇気のいることですけれど……それがあるからこそ、物事はきちんと終わりを迎えられるのですね（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c20",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c21",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c22",
      "text": "「でもさー、全部抱え込むのも無理ゲーじゃない？ブラック化しそう」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c23",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c24",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c25",
      "text": "「そこは分業とのバランス。オーナーは“実行者”ではなく“調整者”。必要に応じて他部署に依頼するが、窓口は一本化する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c26",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c27",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c28",
      "text": "「なるほどね、窓口は固定、中の人が連携する感じか。プレイヤーは変わるけど、操作キャラは同じ、みたいな？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c29",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c2a",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c2b",
      "text": "「いい例えだ。UIは一貫性を保つ、バックエンドで処理を分散する設計」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c2c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c2d",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c2e",
      "text": "「なんだか舞台の裏側のようですわね。表では一人の役者が物語を紡ぎ、裏では多くの人が支えている……」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c2f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c30",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c31",
      "text": "「おお〜文学的〜。じゃあまとめいくよ？りか先生！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c32",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c33",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c34",
      "text": "「要点を整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c35",
      "text": " たらい回し＝",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c36",
      "text": "  責任の曖昧さと構造不備が原因",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c37",
      "text": " 対策＝",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c38",
      "text": "  オーナー制",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c39",
      "text": "  ワンストップ対応",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c3a",
      "text": "  明確な役割設計",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
      "updated": 1773865733
    },
    {
      "id": "69bb0b040000000000957c3b",
      "text": " 重要なのは“利用者視点”の一貫性",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773865733,
